abstract: >
  Mensagem Brasil is a multi-tenant SaaS that delivers personalized, daily
  messages to WhatsApp recipients. Each message is generated by GPT-4o,
  conditioned on per-recipient parameters (name, tone, theme), and
  accompanied by a uniquely generated DALL·E 3 image. The system runs on a
  single x86 cloud instance with a fixed monthly cost of approximately
  US$3.50, decoupled from message volume. The repository documents the
  full architecture, deployment process, prompt design, and lessons learned
  from production deployment.
keywords:
  - large language models
  - controllable text generation
  - prompt engineering
  - multimodal generation
  - applied NLP
  - WhatsApp automation
  - Brazilian Portuguese NLP
